♪ WE'RE RUNNING OVER THE OCEAN

13:37.686 --> 13:40.994
♪ AND FLYIN' TO THE STARS

13:42.952 --> 13:46.390
♪ THERE'S NEVER BEEN SUCH DEVOTION

13:47.914 --> 13:51.047
♪ TO TAKING LOVE THIS FAR

