14:07.672 --> 14:09.370
♪ JUST LIKE IN PARADISE

14:09.500 --> 14:12.852
♪ EVERY SINGLE DAY

14:33.002 --> 14:36.440
♪ WE'RE CHASIN' AFTER THE SUNSHINE

14:37.964 --> 14:41.402
♪ AND WALKIN' ON THE CLOUDS

14:43.099 --> 14:46.363
♪ WE'RE LIVIN' MORE THAN A LIFETIME

14:47.974 --> 14:51.455
♪ AND WE ARE LIVIN' NOW

14:52.021 --> 14:56.373
♪ I KNOW THIS LOVE WE HAVE IS FOREVER ♪

